headline: With Winter Heating Season Nearing, PSEG Long Island Hosts Community Events to Help Customers Struggling with Bills
summary: As winter heating season approaches, PSEG Long Island is holding three community events to help customers apply for state and federal programs that exist to help those struggling with utility bills. There are also many ways they can lower their bills by using energy wisely.

headline: PSEG (PEG) Earnings Expected to Grow: What to Know Ahead of Next Week's Release
